testsuite.name: MIS Leave Management Activities #3

testcase.name: Navigate to Leave Management > Apply tab
Verify fields are Auto Populated by default on Leave tab
Verify From,Till and Reason fields are mandatory fields for Leave Tab
Select From and Till Leave date from Leave Calendar
Verify Total Working Days tooltip from Leave Tab
Choose leave for half day option from Leave tab
Enter required data and click on Submit leave
